org.jruyi.common

Interface ThreadLocalCache.IFactory

  • Enclosing class:
    ThreadLocalCache

    public static interface ThreadLocalCache.IFactory
    A factory class to create instances of IThreadLocalCache. It is used to separate the implementation provider from the API module.
